An '''anti-grav loader''' was a watercraft used for the shipping of goods by [[Water/Legends|water]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[R-Duba]]. It was equipped with an [[anti-gravity unit]] for loading and unloading of heavy goods. [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Kirk Windjammer]] had an anti-grav loader called the ''[[Seaskimmer]]''.

